Anyway, what Wacko Jacko needs is to be sent to a mental facility where he can seek serious help and have it explained to him, no, scratch that, drilled into his fucking psycho skull, that his strange attitude toward children is just getting him into trouble, even if they are innocent because it's fucking weird and people don't understand it.  Nobody's ever heard of somebody who loves children THAT MUCH but isn't a perv.  Unfortunately there are far more pervs then sincere and innocent lovers of children.  He needs to snap out of it, in a huge way.<br>
<br>
He admits fully to sharing beds with children.  In a documentary earlier this year he said (quoted from an article)... &quot;When you say bed you're thinking sexual,&quot; the singer said during the interview. &quot;It's not sexual; we're going to sleep. I tuck them in. ... It's very charming; it's very sweet.&quot;<br>
<br>
O..K..Uhh, yeah, fahh-reak!  I would NEVER let my kid do that...but a small part of me thinks he might actually be sincere albeit extremely abnormal, and is just too naive understand why it's not right.<br>
<br>
So, I guess I'll still give him a small benefit of the doubt, but if he's convicted, I won't be able to listen to his music without feeling sick to my stomach and I hope somebody makes him their prison bitch for life.  Unless he likes it, then somebody just needs to but glass shards in his mashed potatoes because there's no hope. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:verdana;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Tryon Briarwood</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> &lt;<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.xevnull.com">NULL</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->&gt;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
